data.enText: a feeling that you are not pleased and satisfied

data.chText: 许多人表示对这一安排不满。
data.enText: Many people have expressed their dissatisfaction with the arrangement.

tr: the feeling of being displeased and discontent
example: he was never slow to express his dissatisfaction with the service he received

value.def: If you feel dissatisfaction with something, you are not contented or pleased with it.

example.ex: She has already expressed her dissatisfaction with this aspect of the policy...
example.tran: 她对政策的这一方面已经表达了不满。

example.ex: Low pay is the main cause of job dissatisfaction among teachers.
example.tran: 低薪是教师对工作不满的主要原因。
